\c 10
\s Ukuhlalisana kwabathatheneyo
\p
\v 1 Wasesukuma lapho weza emingceleni yeJudiya edabula ngaphetsheya kweJordani; amaxuku asebuya abuthana kuye\x + Mat. 19.1-9.\x*; wasephinda ukubafundisa, njengokwejwayela kwakhe\x + 1.21; 2.13; 4.1; 6.2,6,34; 12.35; 14.49. Mat. 19.2.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Kwasekusiza kuye abaFarisi bambuza \add ukuthi\add*: Kuvunyelwe yini ukuthi indoda yale umka\add yo\add*? bemlinga\x + Joha. 8.6.\x*.
\v 3 Wasephendula wathi kubo: UMozisi walilayani?
\v 4 Basebesithi: UMozisi wavuma ukubhala incwadi yesehlukaniso, loku\add m\add*ala.
\v 5 UJesu wasephendula wathi kubo: Ngenxa yobulukhuni benhliziyo yenu walibhalela lumlayo;
\v 6 kodwa kusukela ekuqaleni kokudaliweyo, uNkulunkulu wabenza owesilisa lowesifazana.
\v 7 Ngenxa yalokhu indoda izatshiya uyise lonina, inamathele kumkayo,
\v 8 njalo labo ababili bazakuba nyamanye\x + Gen. 2.24.\x*. Ngakho kabasebabili, kodwa \add ba\add*nyamanye.
\v 9 Ngakho lokho uNkulunkulu akuhlanganisileyo, kakungabi lamuntu okwehlukanisayo.
\p
\v 10 Endlini abafundi bakhe basebebuya bembuza ngalokhu.
\v 11 Wasesithi kubo: Loba ngubani owala umkakhe athathe omunye, uyafeba kuye;
\v 12 lomfazi uba esala indoda yakhe endele kwenye, uyafeba\x + 1 Kor. 7.13.\x*.
\s Ukubusiswa kwabantwana abancane
\p
\v 13 Basebeletha abantwana abancane kuye ukuze ababambe; kodwa abafundi bakhe babakhuza aba\add ba\add*lethayo.
\v 14 Kodwa uJesu e\add ku\add*bona wathukuthela, wathi kubo: Vumelani abantwana abancane beze kimi\x + Mat. 19.13-15. Luka 18.15-17.\x*, lingabenqabeli. Ngoba umbuso kaNkulunkulu ungowabanje\x + Mat. 18.3.\x*.
\v 15 Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Loba ngubani ongemukeli umbuso kaNkulunkulu njengomntwana omncane, kasoze angene kuwo.
\v 16 Njalo ebagona, ebeka izandla \add zakhe\add* phezu kwabo, wababusisa\x + 9.36.\x*.
\s Ijaha elinothileyo
\p
\v 17 Esephumele endleleni, omunye wa\add m\add*gijimela\x + Mat. 19.16-30. Luka 18.18-30.\x*, eguqa phambi kwakhe wambuza \add wathi\add*: Mfundisi olungileyo, ngingenzani ukuze ngidle ilifa lempilo elaphakade\x + Mat. 18.3.\x*?
\v 18 UJesu wasesithi kuye: Ungibizelani ngokuthi olungileyo? Kakho olungileyo, ngaphandle koyedwa, uNkulunkulu.
\v 19 Uyayazi imilayo \add ethi\add*: Ungafebi, ungabulali, ungebi, ungafakazi amanga\x + Eks. 20.13-16,12.\x*, ungadlelezeli\x + Eks. 20.17.\x*, hlonipha uyihlo lonyoko\x + Eks. 20.12,13-16.\x*.
\v 20 Wasephendula wathi kuye: Mfundisi, lezizinto zonke ngizigcinile kusukela ebutsheni bami.
\v 21 Njalo uJesu emkhangela wamthanda\x + 10.27. Mat. 19.26.\x*, wathi kuye: Kunye okusweleyo; hamba, uthengise konke olakho, uphe abayanga, njalo uzakuba lokuligugu ezulwini; njalo uze, uthathe isiphambano, ungilandele\x + 8.34.\x*.
\v 22 Kodwa edanile ngalelilizwi wasuka wahamba edabukile; ngoba wayelempahla ezinengi.
\p
\v 23 UJesu wasethalaza wathi kubafundi bakhe: Kuzakuba lukhuni kangakanani kwabalenotho ukungena embusweni kaNkulunkulu.
\v 24 Abafundi basebemangala ngamazwi akhe\x + 10.32.\x*. Kodwa uJesu ephendula futhi wathi kubo: Bantwana, kulukhuni kangakanani kwabathembela enothweni ukungena embusweni kaNkulunkulu;
\v 25 kulula ukuthi ikamela lithutshe entunjeni yenalithi, kulokuthi umuntu onothileyo angene embusweni kaNkulunkulu\x + Jobe 31.24. Hlab. 52.7. Zaga 11.28. 1 Tim. 6.17. Hlab. 62.10.\x*.
\v 26 Basebemangala kakhulukazi, bekhulumisana \add bathi\add*: Pho kungasindiswa bani\x + 6.51; 7.37.\x*?
\v 27 UJesu wasebakhangela wathi: Kubantu kakulakwenzeka, kodwa kaku\add njalo\add* kuNkulunkulu; ngoba zonke izinto ziyenzeka kuNkulunkulu\x + 10.27. Mat. 19.26.\x*.
\s Umvuzo wokuzidela
\p
\v 28 UPetro waseqala ukuthi kuye: Khangela, thina sitshiye konke, sakulandela.
\v 29 UJesu wasephendula wathi: Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Kakukho muntu otshiye indlu, kumbe abafowabo, kumbe odadewabo, kumbe uyise, kumbe unina, kumbe umka\add khe\add*, kumbe abantwana, kumbe amasimu, ngenxa yami levangeli,
\v 30 ongayikwemukela ngokwekhulu khathesi ngalesisikhathi, izindlu labafowabo labodadewabo labonina labantwana lamasimu\x + Luka 18.30.\x*, kanye lokuzingelwa, lempilo elaphakade esikhathini esizayo\x + 2 Kor. 12.10. 2 Thes. 1.4. 2 Tim. 3.11. Seb. 14.22.\x*.
\v 31 Kodwa abanengi abokuqala bazakuba ngabokucina, labokucina ngabokuqala.
\s UJesu uphinda akhulume ngokufa lokuvuka kwakhe
\p
\v 32 Njalo babesendleleni besenyukela eJerusalema\x + Mat. 20.17-19. Luka 18.31-34.\x*; uJesu wayesehamba phambi kwabo\x + Luka 9.51; 12.50.\x*, njalo babemangele, belandela babesesaba\x + 10.24.\x*. Wasethatha futhi abalitshumi lambili, waqala ukubatshela izinto ezazizakwenzakala kuye
\v 33 ukuthi: Khangelani, senyukela eJerusalema, futhi iNdodana yomuntu izanikelwa kubapristi abakhulu lakubabhali, njalo bazayigwebela ukufa, bayinikele kwabezizwe,
\v 34 bazayiyangisa, bayitshaye ngesiswepu, bayikhafulele amathe\x + Luka 18.32. Mat. 26.67; 27.30. Mark. 14.65; 15.19.\x*, bayibulale; njalo ngosuku lwesithathu izabuya ivuke \add ekufeni\add*.
\s UJesu ukhuza amadodana kaZebediya
\p
\v 35 Kwasekusiza kuye uJakobe loJohane\x + Mat. 20.20-28.\x*, amadodana kaZebediya\x + Mat. 20.20.\x*, besithi: Mfundisi, sithanda ukuthi usenzele loba yini esizayicela.
\v 36 Wasesithi kubo: Lithanda ukuthi ngilenzeleni?
\v 37 Basebesithi kuye: Siphe ukuthi sihlale omunye ngakwesokunene sakho lomunye ngakwesokhohlo sakho ebukhosini bakho\x + Mat. 18.19.\x*.
\v 38 Kodwa uJesu wathi kubo: Kalikwazi elikucelayo. Linganatha yini inkezo engiyinathayo mina, njalo libhabhathizwe ngobhabhathizo engibhabhathizwa ngalo mina?
\v 39 Basebesithi kuye: Singa\add kwenza\add*. Kodwa uJesu wathi kubo: Isibili inkezo engiyinathayo mina lizayinatha; lizabhabhathizwa ngobhabhathizo engibhabhathizwa ngalo mina;
\v 40 kodwa ukuhlala ngakwesokunene sami langakwesokhohlo sami kayisikho okwami uku\add ku\add*pha, kodwa \add kungo\add*kwalabo abakulungiselweyo.
\s Ubukhulu obuqotho
\p
\v 41 Kwathi sebezwile abalitshumi baqala ukuthukuthela ngoJakobe loJohane.
\v 42 Kodwa uJesu wababizela kuye wathi kubo: Liyazi ukuthi labo okuthiwa babusa izizwe bazibusa ngobulukhuni; lezikhulu zazo zisebenzisa amandla phezu kwazo\x + Luka 22.25-27.\x*.
\v 43 Kodwa akuyikuba njalo phakathi kwenu; kodwa loba ngubani othanda ukuba ngomkhulu phakathi kwenu, kabe yisisebenzi senu;
\v 44 njalo loba ngubani othanda ukuba ngowokuqala phakathi kwenu, kabe yisisebenzi sabo bonke\x + 1 Sam. 2.29; 9.22; 21.7. 2 Lan. 32.33. 2 Kor. 11.5.\x*.
\v 45 Ngoba leNdodana yomuntu kayizanga ukukhonzwa, kodwa ukukhonza, lokunika impilo yayo ibe lihlawulo labanengi.
\s UBartimewu isiphofu
\p
\v 46 Basebefika eJeriko\x + Mat. 20.29-34. Luka 18.35-43.\x*; kwathi esephuma eJeriko, labafundi bakhe, lexuku elikhulu\x + Luka 18.35; 19.1.\x*, indodana kaTimewu, uBartimewu oyisiphofu\x + Mat. 20.30.\x* wayehlezi endleleni ephanza.
\v 47 Kwathi esezwile ukuthi nguJesu weNazaretha, waqala ukumemeza lokuthi: Jesu Ndodana kaDavida, akungihawukele\x + 5.41.\x*!
\v 48 Abanengi basebemkhuza ukuthi athule; kodwa wamemeza kakhulukazi, \add esithi\add*: Ndodana kaDavida, akungihawukele\x + Mat. 20.31. Luka 18.39.\x*!
\v 49 UJesu esima wasesithi kabizwe; basebesibiza isiphofu, besithi kuso: Mana isibindi; sukuma, uyakubiza.
\v 50 Sasesilahla isembatho saso sasukuma seza kuJesu.
\v 51 UJesu wasephendula wathi kuso: Ufuna ukuthi ngikwenzeleni? Isiphofu sasesisithi kuye: \w Raboni\w**\x + Joha. 20.16.\x*, ukuthi ngibuye ngibone.
\v 52 UJesu wasesithi kuso: Hamba; ukholo lwakho\x + Mat. 9.2.\x* lukusindisile. Njalo sahle sabuye sabona, salandela uJesu endleleni\x + Mat. 9.22. Mark. 5.34. Luka 8.48; 17.19. Seb. 4.9. Joha. 11.12. Seb. 14.9.\x*.
